OL,3,CMan charged after attack during
OL,4,CBirmingham Pride celebrations
OL,6,FA man has been charged over an assault
OL,7,Fthat took place in a city centre pub
OL,8,Fduring celebrations.
OL,10,F23-year-old Jack Dalton, from
OL,11,FBirmingham, was arrested following the
OL,12,Fincident at a pub in Hurst Street,
OL,13,Fnear the Arcadian, on Friday night (24
OL,14,FMay).
OL,16,FPolice were called to the pub at
OL,17,Fapproximately 6pm where they were told
OL,18,Fthat a man had assaulted several
OL,19,Fpeople inside the venue and had left
OL,20,Fthe scene.
