OL,3,CMan charged after attack during
OL,4,CBirmingham Pride celebrations
OL,6,FPolice say they are treating the
OL,7,Fincident as a hate crime.
OL,9,FThree men, aged 30, 31 and 34, were
OL,10,Fassaulted and their injuries are not
OL,11,Fbelieved to be serious or life
OL,12,Fthreatening.
OL,14,FDalton has been remanded in custody
OL,15,Fand will appear before Birmingham
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow (27 May).
OL,18,Fsays the assault happened during their
OL,19,Fpolicing and partner operation for
OL,20,FBirmingham Pride this weekend.
