OL,4,CBirmingham Pride celebrations
OL,6,FChief Inspector Richard Evans, from
OL,7,FBirmingham police, said: "We will not
OL,8,Ftolerate hate crime in our city.
OL,10,F"People should be able to visit the
OL,11,Fcity without fear of being subjected
OL,12,Fto violence and threats.
OL,14,F"Planning for Pride takes place months
OL,15,Fin advance and the focus is to provide
OL,16,Fa highly visible presence around the
OL,17,FPride site, to make people feel safe
OL,18,Fand to prevent crime.
