OL,6,F"We take hate crime very seriously and
OL,7,Fwould encourage people to come forward
OL,8,Fif they've experienced a hate crime.
OL,10,F"While we'd prefer victims to come to
OL,11,Fus directly, we know that for a
OL,12,Fvariety of reasons, some people do not
OL,13,Fwant to speak with officers preferring
OL,14,Fto report crimes anonymously or not at
OL,15,Fall."
